title: OCE jungle tier IV / III looking for Clash team February 23rd
body:
Hi there,

Didn't make it in time today.
But plan on joining tomorrow (23rd).
I play jungle only.
You can add me in game "Nallodyret".
I have a Clash record of 8-0 (2-0 back in 1st clash due to clash crash & and two 3-0 victories) with my EUW team.
I am currently travelling around Bali, Indonesia.
Hence the need to play on the Oceanic server.
I play in low Platinum on the EUW and EUNE servers - don't know what that corresponds to here.
I have played LoL for more than 7 years, so I know the game fairly well.
Hope to hear back from you.

Best regards,
Nallodyret
